Leadbetter beach is the ideal spot to get one of the greatest views of Santa Barbara. The mountains, the pier the overall scenario is ideal when your out surfing in the beautiful water. Surfing at this location in just absolutely amazing! I can picture it now!

In the case of bad weather or surf conditions and there are no waves at Leadbetter, we'll inform you beforehand regarding the alternative beach either Santa Claus beach or Mondos .)